parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear coil spring can cause the vehicle to sag, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle sags or leans to one side
the rear coil spring is broken or cracked
the vehicle makes a loud noise or clunking sound
the vehicle's handling is affected
the vehicle's ride is bumpy or unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front lower control arm can cause the vehicle to vibrate or shimmy, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates or shimmies
the front lower control arm is broken or worn out
the vehicle's handling is affected
the vehicle's ride is bumpy or unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Oil Consumption and CV Joint Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive oil consumption and CV joint failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents or engine failure.
symptoms: The vehicle consumes excessive oil
the CV joint is worn out or broken
the vehicle's power is reduced
the vehicle's ride is bumpy or unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ODS can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, leading to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag off warning light illuminates
the passenger airbag is disabled
the seatbelt warning chime sounds even when the seat is empty
and the SRS airbag system warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine failure, causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also result in expensive repairs and maintenance.
symptoms: The check oil light illuminates frequently
requiring the addition of oil between oil changes
excessive oil consumption (up to 1-2 quarts per 2000 miles)
and low oil levels.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling and loss of power can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The engine stalls or loses power while driving
often accompanied by warning lights on the dashboard
and may require frequent restarting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission issues can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and may result in expensive repairs.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
causing the vehicle to jerk or stutter
and may result in loss of power or stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition and electrical issues can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and may result in expensive repairs.
symptoms: The engine fails to start
the vehicle stalls
or there are issues with the electrical system
including warning lights on the dashboard.
